item.title: Tue, 27 Oct 2020 08:47:37 UTC
item.description:
Hi Folks,
I've come to the decision to stop releasing the next packages,
due to Alien's choice not to recompile Ktown against  Python 3.9.0.
As I use the latter I would be no longer able to carry out appropriate
testing in the clean installation phase.
The current situation will change as soon as Pat adds Plasma5 to the current.
I'm sorry for my bad english. Happy slacking!
